	  continue reading, you just use the Page-Down key to get the next
	  screenful of text, until you finally get to the end.  When you are at
	  the end, the world will resume auto-scrolling when new text comes in,
	  until the next time a screenful arrives without user input.  If you
	  enter a command in a world, it assumes that you've read all the text
	  that is currently showing, and will allow that text to scroll off the
	  top of the screen before it stops scrolling again.} Para
